snippet: As a reproductive health bill advances in the Philippines, it is peak baby-delivery season, with women and their newborns are sleeping two to a bed at one Manila hospital.
abstract: Reproductive health bill is advancing in Philippines that would require sex education and subsidize birth control; meanwhile, it is peak baby-delivery season and one overcrowded Manila hospital is coping with women and their newborns sleeping two to a bed.
lead_paragraph: As a reproductive health bill advances in the Philippines, it is peak baby-delivery season, with women and their newborns are sleeping two to a bed at one Manila hospital.

headline.seo: Manila Hospital Awaits Reproductive Health Bill’s Fate
headline.main: Manila Hospital, No Stranger to Stork, Awaits Reproductive Health Bill’s Fate
